## Musts

- Multi‑stage builds; small, trusted base images; pin versions (avoid `latest`).
- Non‑root user; no SSH; no build‑time secrets left in layers.
- Use `.dockerignore`; HEALTHCHECK for services.

## CI

- Build and scan images in CI; SBOM/artifact retention.
